.TH bartos 1  "bartos 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
bartos \- Central job scheduling server; receives job data from bartoc instances
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbartos\fR [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR]... [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR]... [\fB\-e\fR|\fB\-\-enable\-std\-output\fR] [\fB\-c\fR|\fB\-\-config\-absolute\-path\fR] [\fB\-t\fR|\fB\-\-tracing\-absolute\-path\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Central job scheduling server; receives job data from bartoc instances
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Turn up logging verbosity (multiple will turn it up more)
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Turn down logging verbosity (multiple will turn it down more)
.TP
\fB\-e\fR, \fB\-\-enable\-std\-output\fR
Enable logging to stdout/stderr
.TP
\fB\-c\fR, \fB\-\-config\-absolute\-path\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Specify the absolute path to the config file
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-tracing\-absolute\-path\fR \fI<PATH>\fR
Specify the absolute path to the tracing output file
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
